        "TileImage": "$($repository a9414165-6806-4a48-8473-49f2747d59b0).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47.\rWe are tasked with eliminating  Mukul Jaywant who has a contract out for his assasination. His coworkers want him gone as he has refused to shower for weeks.\rMr. Wazir Kale is [Redacted] it is of crucial importance that he die by falling as that is what was requested of our client his wife. She is quoted saying this: &quot;I wish Wazir would trip and fall, breaking his bones . He is always out on the streets of Mumbai, leaving me alone to wonder where he gone. I deserve better.&quot;",
